{"id":649988,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/07/撒韬-悼念他/","date":"2020-07-13T22:48:18Z","modified":"2020-07-13T22:48:18Z","title":"撒韬 | 悼念他","content":"<p>那些微信的蜡烛符号是不算数的真情假意。</p>\n<p>今天，我买一根蜡烛，看它燃烧完。</p>\n<p>用这个悼念他。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-649989\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念1-14-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"666\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念1-14-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念1-14-769x1024.jpg 769w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念1-14-768x1023.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念1-14.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>他是我年轻时的兄长，他是我对于国族希望的最后想象与寄托，之后，再没了，再没什么宏大的愿景值得让我向往。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-649990\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念2-3-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"666\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念2-3-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念2-3-769x1024.jpg 769w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念2-3-768x1023.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念2-3.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>为这个最后的勇敢的人，今夜心怀悲痛与哀伤，我们丢失的不仅是他的肉身，更是无数人的灵魂。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-649991\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念3-3-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"666\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念3-3-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念3-3-769x1024.jpg 769w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念3-3-768x1023.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念3-3.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>多说什么都没意思，不懂的人继续不懂，我怀疑那些忙着加班删除的人也不懂。那个比所有人都更品尝着悲痛况味的姐姐在柏林，那个蒙着绷带的头颅是这片大地的骄傲，是那些蒙面封嘴的人的耻辱。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-649992\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念4-3-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"666\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念4-3-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念4-3-769x1024.jpg 769w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念4-3-768x1023.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念4-3.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>干嘛老想着熄灭之后黑暗的可怖，让我们在有最后一点光的时候，认真享受光，聆听光，被光温暖。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-649993\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念5-4-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"666\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念5-4-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念5-4-769x1024.jpg 769w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念5-4-768x1023.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/悼念5-4.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>然而，即使在蜡炬成灰，泪不干的时刻，也请每个人记住，审美，只有审美才能换来人的自由。为了活着的活着，其实已经死去，那些死去仍然被记住的名字，即使敏感不能直接说出，他们永远活着。</p>\n<p>节哀姐姐，安息兄长。</p>\n","author":1067,"categories":[18271,38912,38985],"tags":[9041,19986]}